name: P R I D E 🌈
description:
“It is absolutely imperative that every human being’s freedom and human rights are respected, all over the world.” - Former Icelandic Prime Minister Jóhanna Sigurðardóttir
Rainbows are so beautiful. And so are You. "You are beautiful, No matter What they say". This artwork is dedicated to all the beautiful people in the world, who love beyond any boundaries. You all are the strongest person in this whole Universe. Hats off to you.
